<div class="about-hero text-center">
    <div class="container">
        <h1 class="about-title">Our Story. Our Passion.</h1>
        <p class="lead text-muted" style="max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; font-size: 20px;">We didn't just start a store; we started a movement to redefine modern elegance for everyone.</p>
    </div>
</div>

<section class="about-story-section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row align-items-center">
            <div class="col-lg-6 mb-5 mb-lg-0">
                <div style="background: #eee; height: 500px; border-radius: 20px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; overflow: hidden; position: relative;">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1441986300917-64674bd600d8?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1000" alt="Fashion Journey" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover;">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6 ps-lg-5">
                <h2 style="font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 25px; font-size: 32px;">The FashionKart Journey</h2>
                <div class="story-content">
                    <p>Founded in 2018, FashionKart was born out of a simple realization: the fashion industry was divided between overpriced luxury and low-quality fast fashion. We saw a void that needed to be filled—a space for high-quality, thoughtfully designed clothing that remains accessible to those who value style over labels.</p>
                    <p>What started as a small collection of 10 signature pieces curated in a Mumbai studio has evolved into a global brand. Today, we serve over 100,000 customers worldwide, but our core philosophy remains unchanged: <strong>Style is a right, not a luxury.</strong></p>
                    <p>Every piece in our collection is a testament to our commitment to craftsmanship. We source the finest fabrics and work with ethical workshops to ensure that every stitch tells a story of quality and integrity.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="highlight-strip text-center">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="stat-box">
                    <h3>2018</h3>
                    <p>Year Founded</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="stat-box">
                    <h3>100K+</h3>
                    <p>Happy Customers</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="stat-box">
                    <h3>50+</h3>
                    <p>Designer Collabs</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="about-story-section" style="background: #fff;">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row text-center mb-5">
            <div class="col-12">
                <h2 style="font-weight: 800; font-size: 32px;">Why Choose FashionKart?</h2>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                <div class="mission-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-gem mb-4" style="font-size: 30px; color: #e53637;"></i>
                    <h4 style="font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 15px;">Quality First</h4>
                    <p class="text-muted">We don't compromise. Every product undergoes a 12-point quality check before it reaches your doorstep.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                <div class="mission-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-leaf mb-4" style="font-size: 30px; color: #e53637;"></i>
                    <h4 style="font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 15px;">Sustainable Style</h4>
                    <p class="text-muted">We are committed to reducing our carbon footprint through eco-friendly packaging and conscious sourcing.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                <div class="mission-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-users mb-4" style="font-size: 30px; color: #e53637;"></i>
                    <h4 style="font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 15px;">Community Focus</h4>
                    <p class="text-muted">Our designs are inspired by you. We listen to our community to create pieces you'll actually want to wear.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

